flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Problem[Problem Framing<br/>Business Context, Constraints, Metrics]
    
    Problem --> Design[System Design & Implementation]
    Design --> DesignData[Data & Knowledge Design]
    Design --> DesignNetwork[Agent Network Design]
    Design --> DesignPrompt[Prompt & Policy Design]
    Design --> DesignModel[Model Selection]
    
    DesignData --> Implementation[Implementation]
    DesignNetwork --> Implementation
    DesignPrompt --> Implementation
    DesignModel --> Implementation
    
    Implementation --> Evaluation[Evaluation]
    Evaluation --> EvalRun[Run Evaluations]
    EvalRun --> EvalAnalyze[Identify Issues]
    EvalAnalyze --> EvalRefine[Refine Prompts/Models/Logic]
    EvalRefine --> EvalRun
    
    EvalAnalyze -->|Quality Threshold Met| Deploy[Deployment]
    EvalRefine -.->|Iterate| Implementation
    
    Deploy --> DeployConfig[Pre-Deployment Config]
    DeployConfig --> DeployCI[CI/CD Integration]
    DeployCI --> DeployProd[Production Deployment]
    
    DeployProd --> AgentOps[AgentOps<br/>Observability & Operations]
    AgentOps --> Observe[LangSmith Traces & Threads]
    AgentOps --> Monitor[Monitoring & Alerting]
    AgentOps --> Debug[Trace Analysis]
    
    Observe --> PostDeploy[Post-Deployment<br/>Monitoring & Governance]
    Monitor --> PostDeploy
    Debug --> PostDeploy
    
    PostDeploy --> Feedback[Collect Feedback]
    Feedback --> Governance[Governance & Audit]
    Governance --> Continuous[Continuous Improvement]
    
    Continuous -->|Refine| Design
    Continuous -->|Optimize| AgentOps
    Continuous -->|Enhance| PostDeploy
    
